## Non-Goals (Do NOT Build)

- Full BI warehouse platform
- Warehouse-native semantic layer product
- Multi-tenant hosted analytics service
- iframe-based embedded whole-app clone
- Tight dependency on dbt, Rill, ClickHouse, or any single modeling system

## Context Recovery

1. Read docs/status/master-plan.md for current phase
2. Read docs/adr/ for architecture decisions
3. Read AGENTS.md for agent coordination model
4. Check git log --oneline -20 for recent activity
